1
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:57,880
Dr. Jiang.

2
00:00:58,359 --> 00:00:59,280
Dr. Jiang.

3
00:00:59,479 --> 00:01:00,280
Dr. Jiang.

4
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:06,680
He's so handsome.

5
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,719
This doctor is so handsome.

6
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,280
This is our new doctor.

7
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,799
Dr. Jiang's here.

8
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,159
I know you're quite impressive.

9
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,439
You should've seen him drunk.

10
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,319
It took several of us to even lift him.

11
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,439
I brought you breakfast.

12
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,760
Let's grab BBQ when you're done.

13
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,319
You've got to drink with him sometime.

14
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:25,879
Hold on.

15
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,599
Wait.

16
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,599
What's his problem anyway?

17
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,319
Is there a misunderstanding between you?

18
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,239
Why's he always targeting you?

19
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,519
Move.

20
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,400
We're gonna miss it.

21
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,120
Maybe he's afraid

22
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,040
I'll spill coffee on him again.

23
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:52,439
You're going to the fourth floor too?

24
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,480
Hey, you.

25
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,879
Do you still remember me?

26
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:02,959
We just met yesterday.

27
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,159
Pediatric dentistry, Pei Xi.

28
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,959
It's me. Remember?

29
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:17,120
The expert from a top hospital.

30
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:18,960
Are you always a man of few words?

31
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,439
How about we add each other on WeChat?

32
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:22,439
First,

33
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,520
my name isn't "hey."

34
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,360
Second,

35
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,719
I'm not some expert.

36
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,879
I'm just an attending doctor.

37
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,360
Third,

38
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,000
I don't like being around chatty people.

39
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,879
Especially you.

40
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:30,919
Fourth,

41
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,520
as a doctor,

42
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:34,800
even if it's not your specialty,

43
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,360
in a situation like yesterday's,

44
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,080
you should possess

45
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,719
basic first-aid skills,

46
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,439
unlike you and your colleague,

47
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:42,360
who panicked and fumbled around.

48
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,680
Damn.

49
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:48,360
His logic is sharper than my dental molds.

50
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:49,680
I haven't even left yet.

51
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,439
How many times have I told you?

52
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,759
Be attentive and focused.

53
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,680
Stay completely focused.

54
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,800
Treat patients like your own parents.

55
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,759
Block out all distractions.

56
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,400
Treat them wholeheartedly.

57
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,080
Jiang.

58
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,039
Nice work in surgery yesterday.

59
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,240
A talent like you

60
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:14,520
coming to Mei'en Hospital,

61
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:16,000
certainly came to the right place.

62
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:17,439
You should be

63
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,960
in the right position,

64
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,479
shining and thriving.

65
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,159
Look at this.

66
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:25,879
Why the General Dentistry Department?

67
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,159
General Dentistry Department is great.

68
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:31,919
General Dentistry Department is the core.

69
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,400
So many beg me for it, but I turn them down.

70
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,280
I'm sorry.

71
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,800
I won't accept it.

72
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,719
Are you refusing it,

73
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,000
or are you too scared?

74
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,759
Maxillofacial Surgery.

75
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,520
Otherwise, no deal.

76
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:56,599
Young man,

77
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,400
don't mistake a platform for ability.

78
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,680
Truly talented people

79
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,800
reach the peak wherever they stand.

80
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,240
Just General Dentistry Department.

81
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,479
Take it or

82
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,039
leave.

83
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,959
You little punk.

84
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,360
Trying to act tough with me?

85
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,279
You're still too green.

86
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,319
How did he end up in our department?

87
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,920
Everything about him annoys me.

88
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,240
Just look at the way he walks.

89
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:58,839
I know, right?

90
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,639
Looking at us with his nose in the air.

91
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,879
Who does he think he is? - Right.

92
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,560
Qiao Qiyue, what's all the gossip about?

93
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,480
Code Red! Code Red!

94
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:06,800
Stop being so dramatic.

95
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,160
The guy walking with his nose in the air.

96
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,160
He's coming to our department.

97
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,319
Who?

98
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:12,480
You know, that one.

99
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,279
Genius Jiang.

100
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,199
He's coming to our department.

101
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,879
Doctor, take a look at my tooth.

102
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,879
Chipped it opening a bottle yesterday.

103
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,920
See if you can help.

104
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:25,680
Can you just glue it back on?

105
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,920
I've got plans tonight.

106
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:28,759
Your tooth is split like firewood.

107
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,120
Glue won't hold it.

108
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:31,600
Cut down on smoking and drinking.

109
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:32,480
It has to come out.

110
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,360
It has to come out.

111
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:35,199
No way. My boyfriend said

112
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,560
my wisdom tooth is in a lucky spot.

113
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,839
Pulling it will ruin my fortune.

114
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:40,000
Just give me painkillers and antibiotics.

115
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,839
Better treat your lovesick brain first.

116
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,360
Get a new boyfriend before coming back.

117
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,399
Doctor,

118
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:47,000
do you have to make it sound so serious?

119
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,560
Back home, for heat-induced toothaches,

120
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:52,560
drinking herbal tea works really well.

121
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:54,920
You have pulpitis caused by a cavity.

122
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,480
Without root canal treatment,

123
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:58,000
all your teeth will rot away.

124
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,959
By then, no magic potion can save you.

125
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:05,040
Root canal treatment,

126
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:07,319
magic potion,

127
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:09,279
I'll need both of them.

128
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:20,079
Dr. Jiang in General Dentistry Department

129
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,639
is truly a waste of his talent.

130
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:22,800
Glad you know it.

131
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:40,920
Dr. Jiang, I apologize again.

132
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:42,439
I really didn't mean to

133
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,639
get your clothes dirty yesterday.

134
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,800
And I didn't mean to take advantage of you.

135
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,600
You really don't need to avoid me.

136
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,120
As colleagues,

137
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:51,120
let's just call it even between us.

138
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:51,800
How about it?

139
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,800
I'll take your silence as a yes.

140
00:06:57,480 --> 00:07:00,000
Dr. Jiang, could you help a colleague out

141
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:01,319
and keep a secret?

142
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,279
You can rest assured.

143
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:07,959
I have zero interest in any of

144
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,560
the boring things around here.

145
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,480
Including you.

146
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,959
Do you feel like you've been wronged?

147
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,319
Like the operating table is the only place

148
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,560
where you can prove your worth?

149
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,240
Let's make a bet.

150
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,279
If not for Director Zeng's arrangement,

151
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:29,360
you wouldn't qualify for our department.

152
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,199
Do you believe me?

153
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,600
You don't?

154
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,199
Fine.

155
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,399
If you can brush these teeth clean today,

156
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,439
I'll take over all your patients from now on.

157
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,639
How about it?

158
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,839
Dare to bet?

159
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:49,759
Who exactly are you trying to humiliate?

160
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,079
Dr. Jiang

161
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:23,120
Is the toothbrush we have here

162
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,240
not quite right for your teeth?

163
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,759
How about I get you a different one?

164
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:28,360
Use the dental plaque toothpaste.

165
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,600
A bet's a bet.

166
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:32,679
Brushing longer doesn't mean

167
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,879
your teeth are cleaner.

168
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,519
Open up.

169
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,039
Open up.

170
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:47,080
The Bass method.

171
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,600
Angle the brush 45 degrees to the gums.

172
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,159
Brush upward on the lower teeth.

173
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:52,759
Brush downward on the upper teeth.

174
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:55,720
If you can't control the vibration well,

175
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:58,000
make small circles on the chewing surfaces.

176
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,919
But never scrub side to side.
